sentences.english: Conclusion Complex treatment is the most effective method for treatment of residual brun wound.
sentences.chinese: 結論綜合治療是治療燒傷殘餘創面的重要方法。

sentences.english: That's according to a new AP Ipsos poll.
sentences.chinese: 這是根據最新的美聯社依普索民意調查得出的結論。

sentences.english: Conclusions Uterine cavity and fallopian tube abnormalities were the important reason of female infertile.
sentences.chinese: 結論子宮腔及輸卵管形態異常是不孕症的重要原因。

sentences.english: Conclusion Mutations in the CYP1B1 gene have genetic heterogeneity.
sentences.chinese: 結論CYP1B1基因具有明顯的遺傳異質性。

sentences.english: Conclusions Osteoclast-mediated bone resorption was inhibited by the bisphosphonate administration.
sentences.chinese: 結論雙膦酸鹽對破骨細胞性骨吸收有明顯的抑制作用。

sentences.english: Conclusion The above procedure is necessary for the ankle sprains with the injury of the common peroneal nerve.
sentences.chinese: 結論踝扭傷出現腓總神經損傷者應作探查鬆解減壓術。

sentences.english: Conclusion Heavy-moxibustion is a good method for constipation after stroke.
sentences.chinese: 結論重灸法是治療中風後便祕的良好方法。

sentences.english: Conclusion Tibia fracture healing delays after ovariectomy.
sentences.chinese: 結論卵巢切除後，脛骨骨折癒合緩慢。

sentences.english: Purpose To study limb immobilization influencing on denervated muscle atrophy.
sentences.chinese: 結論肢體制動加速了失神經支配肌肉萎縮的發展。

sentences.english: The results provide empirical foundation for model-building and simulations.
sentences.chinese: 結論爲進一步建模仿真提供了實證基礎。

sentences.english: Conclusions It was proved feasibility of DNA fingerprints in the heredity monitoring of inbred strain rat.
sentences.chinese: 結論證實了該方法在近交系大鼠遺傳監測中的可行性。

sentences.english: If the conclusions can not be applied in practice, better dump them when it is still early.

sentences.english: This conclusion plays an important theoretical guiding role in ESG designing and testing.
sentences.chinese: 其結論對靜電陀螺儀的設計與測試具有理論指導意義。

sentences.english: Conclusions Up till now, the operation pattern for ectopic IUD is not definite .

sentences.english: Conclusion These results suggest that benidipine is a safe and effective anti-hypertension drug.
sentences.chinese: 結論貝尼地平是一種安全有效的抗高血壓藥。

sentences.english: At last that RFID is IT Pioneer is concluded.
sentences.chinese: 最後本文得出RFID是IT“尖兵”的結論。
